Bring 1 cup water to boiling in microwavable glass measuring cup, about 2 minutes on High. Stir in cardamom; let steep 5 minutes. Place tea bag in drinking cup or mug; slowly pour hot water into cup, leaving behind settled cardamom on bottom of measuring cup. Let tea steep 1 to 2 minutes. Dunk bag several times; discard. Stir in honey.